<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Issue Converting Mike Tyson's Punch-Out!! to MMC3 *CHR*]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=10741&amp;p=121750#p121750"><![CDATA[
You need to figure out what part of the code is inserting FD/FE tiles and what scanlines they occur on, and then set an IRQ to fire at those times. You may have to do some bank rearranging if more than one switch occurs during a scanline or if it draws sprites from both pattern tables.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat Nov 30, 2013 11:33 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
